## JOB TITLE
Staff Backend Engineer

## COMPANY
CloudInnovate Solutions

## DESCRIPTION
We are looking for a Staff Backend Engineer to join our platform team and lead the architecture of our next-generation distributed systems. You will work on high-scale infrastructure handling millions of requests per day, mentoring a team of engineers, and making key architectural decisions.

This is a high-impact role where you will influence the technical direction of the company. You'll work closely with product and infrastructure teams to design and implement scalable, reliable systems.

## REQUIRED SKILLS
- 8+ years of backend development experience
- Expertise in Go or Rust (primary)
- Deep understanding of distributed systems and microservices
- Experience with Kubernetes and container orchestration
- Strong knowledge of databases (PostgreSQL, NoSQL)
- Experience with cloud platforms (AWS, GCP, or Azure)
- Leadership and mentoring capabilities
- System design and architecture skills

## RESPONSIBILITIES
- Design and implement scalable backend services
- Lead architectural discussions and decisions
- Mentor junior and mid-level engineers
- Conduct code reviews and maintain code quality standards
- Collaborate with product team to deliver features
- Participate in on-call rotation and incident response
- Optimize system performance and reliability
